  <div id="mainarea_scrollable">
    <div id="mainarea_center">
      <div id="part_left">
  <h1>10$&nbsp;(USD), and that&prime;s all!</h1>
  <button id="change_currency_button" title="Change currency" type="button" onclick="Dialog.showDialog('currency_dialog_content')">Change currency</button>
  <p>With a unique payment of <strong>10$&nbsp;(USD)</strong>, enjoy <strong>unlimited downloads</strong> and unlock the soundfont library in Polyphone.</p>
  <form id="premium_form" method="post">
    <input type="hidden" name="amount" value="10">
    <input type="hidden" name="currency" value="USD">
    <button class="button" name="action_name" value = "premium.paypal" title="Get a Premium account"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 576 512"><path d="M309 106c11.4-7 19-19.7 19-34c0-22.1-17.9-40-40-40s-40 17.9-40 40c0 14.4 7.6 27 19 34L209.7 220.6c-9.1 18.2-32.7 23.4-48.6 10.7L72 160c5-6.7 8-15 8-24c0-22.1-17.9-40-40-40S0 113.9 0 136s17.9 40 40 40c.2 0 .5 0 .7 0L86.4 427.4c5.5 30.4 32 52.6 63 52.6H426.6c30.9 0 57.4-22.1 63-52.6L535.3 176c.2 0 .5 0 .7 0c22.1 0 40-17.9 40-40s-17.9-40-40-40s-40 17.9-40 40c0 9 3 17.3 8 24l-89.1 71.3c-15.9 12.7-39.5 7.5-48.6-10.7L309 106z"/></svg>
<span>Get a Premium account</span></button>
    <a href="/en/premium?currency=USD&price=15" class="after_button" rel="nofollow">More expensive, please!</a>
  </form>
  <p>By clicking on the button, you will be redirected to the PayPal website. You can then pay using your PayPal balance or credit card.</p>
  <p>Once the payment has been made, simply go to the Polyphone settings and enter the email address and password associated with your account to unlock the library (see this <a href='/en/documentation/manual/settings#doc_library'>page</a> for more details).</p>
</div><div id="part_right">
  <img src="/images/library_en.jpg">
</div>


